text: María José Urrutia Sánchez (born 17 December 1993) is a Chilean footballer who plays as a forward for Brazilian club AE 3B da Amazônia and the Chile women's national team. ==International career== Urrutia represented Chile at the 2010 FIFA U-17 Women's World Cup. ==Personal life== Urrutia has a daughter, whom she gave birth in 2014. == References == Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Chilean women's footballers Category:Women's association football forwards Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Club Deportivo Palestino (women) players Category:Chile women's international footballers Category:Chilean expatriate women's footballers Category:Chilean expatriate sportspeople in Brazil Category:Expatriate women's footballers in Brazil Category:2019 FIFA Women's World Cup players
title: María José Urrutia
